By Daniels Ekugo The Light Duty Truck segment in the Nigerian automobile market is going to witness a turnaround as Weststar Associates Limited, Authorised General Distributor for Mercerdes Benz in Nigeria has unveiled its Mercedes-Benz Accelo truck. The company explained that following its successful launch in 2017, the Mercedes-Benz Accelo has “carved its niche in the light-duty commercial vehicle truck segment in Nigeria.. This is in line with the ever increasing pressure on businesses to increase efficiency, reduce operating costs and grow revenues”. Do you have something awesome to share with the world? Click here to share Do you ever have any question about anything you wish to ask and get answer? Click here to ask Follow us on twitter @NigeriaTodayNG Also, Like us on facebook This post was syndicated from The NEWS. Click here to read the full text on the original website.